==Colonies and Outposts==
</div>Since you enter this level, you are alone. Therefore, no colonies or outposts are possible.

How good! Remember that ''Almond Ocean'' at [[Level 259]] ?{{Underline}}<div class="title">
==Entrances and Exits==
</div>
==== Entrances ====
One may get into this level from almost all levels and sub-levels in the Backrooms. Some of the ways include:
{{Blurimage|file=hll for lvl sky.png|caption=Entrance at Level 99.|align=right}}
*Walk into the black square illusion at [[Level 99]] when one sees urban skyscrapers with a thick layer of fog.
*Noclipping at any levels except [[Level 0]].
*Find a graffiti at [[Level 1]] that says "Follow me".
*Find two doors at a random level. Choose the correct door will bring one here.
{{Blurimage|file=lv270_entrance.jpg|caption=An entrance at Level ????????|align=right}}
==== Exits ====
*Taking a huge leap from the Ultimate Skyscraper may noclip one to [[Level 280]]. However, most of the time, one wakes up at this level again.













